

 before running acoFoam - Pekeris_Waveguide case: 

 run blockMesh - to build the mesh
 run setFields - to assign cf (speed of sound) and rhof (density) values 
 
 set or check constant/SourceParameters
 set or check constant/CPLMParameters
 

 Recommendations

- Grid cells must be orthogonal, with a maximum non-orthogonality of 60.

- The CPLM layer must be at least two wavelengths thick.

- We used 15 grid points per wavelength, a coarser mesh may lead to high numerical dispersion effects.

- The Courant number should remain below 0.5. It is automatically evaluated and printed when acoFoam starts running.
